</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A12436C9D37BFFEFFCB8FC0A1D266FFB" blockId="4.[831,1437,257,1571]" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFCB8FC0A1D1C6987" bold="true" box="[831,1142,998,1023]" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">Rapports et différences</emphasis>
: L’espèce est proche d’ 
<taxonomicName id="669B4D4AD37BFFEFFCD1FBEA1D0C6E66" box="[854,1126,1031,1055]" class="Ostracoda" family="Cytheridae" genus="Asymmetricythere" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="4" pageNumber="148" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="undefined-1">
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFCD1FBEA1D7C6E66" box="[854,1046,1031,1055]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">Asymmetricythere</emphasis>
sp. 1
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFBFEFBE51DDE6E66" box="[1145,1204,1032,1055]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">sensu</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="C50A4B38D37BFFEFFB40FBEA1CF66E66" author="CARBONNEL" box="[1223,1436,1031,1055]" pageId="4" pageNumber="148" pagination="33 - 243" refId="ref7047" refString="CARBONNEL, G. (1986) - Ostracodes tertiaires (Paleogene a Neogene) du bassin senegalo-guineen. Documents du Bureau de Recherches Geologique et Minieres, Orleans, 101: 33 - 243." type="journal article" year="1986">CARBONNEL, 1986</bibRefCitation>
(Eocène inférieur et moyen de Casamance et 
<collectingCountry id="D98C7659D37BFFEFFAC8FBCA1CF66E46" box="[1359,1436,1063,1087]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">Guinée</collectingCountry>
<collectingRegion id="635FF82BD37BFFEFFCC7FBAA1AE66E26" box="[832,908,1095,1119]" country="Guinea-Bissau" name="Bissau" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">Bissau</collectingRegion>
). Elle s’en distingue par les côtes moins marquées, l’espace intercostal ponctué, l’expansion foliacée plus marquée et la présence d’une empreinte oculaire. 
<taxonomicName id="669B4D4AD37BFFEFFCC7FB441A866EB9" authorityName="S" authorityYear="2012" box="[832,1004,1192,1216]" class="Ostracoda" family="Cytheridae" genus="Asymmetricythere" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="4" pageNumber="148" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semoupathei">
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFCC7FB441A866EB9" box="[832,1004,1192,1216]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">A. semoupathei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est également proche d’ 
<taxonomicName id="669B4D4AD37BFFEFFA97FB441D0F6E99" authority="BASSIOUNI &amp; LUGER, 1996" authorityName="BASSIOUNI &amp; LUGER" authorityYear="1996" class="Ostracoda" family="Cytheridae" genus="Asymmetricythere" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="4" pageNumber="148" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tricostata">
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFA97FB441CF66EB9" box="[1296,1436,1193,1216]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">A. tricostata</emphasis>
BASSIOUNI &amp; LUGER, 1996
</taxonomicName>
(Eocène moyen de 
<collectingCountry id="D98C7659D37BFFEFFABBFB251CFF6E99" box="[1340,1429,1224,1248]" name="Somalia" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">Somalie</collectingCountry>
) mais s’en distingue par sa taille plus petite, des côtes plus nombreuses et le bord dorsal plus fortement incliné. 
<taxonomicName id="669B4D4AD37BFFEFFCC7FAC71A866F38" authorityName="S" authorityYear="2012" box="[832,1004,1321,1345]" class="Ostracoda" family="Cytheridae" genus="Asymmetricythere" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="4" pageNumber="148" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semoupathei">
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFCC7FAC71A866F38" box="[832,1004,1321,1345]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">A. semoupathei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est également plus petite et possède moins de côtes qu’ 
<taxonomicName id="669B4D4AD37BFFEFFB8EFAA41A1F6FFB" authority="BASSIOUNI, 1971" authorityName="BASSIOUNI" authorityYear="1971" class="Ostracoda" family="Cytheridae" genus="Asymmetricythere" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="4" pageNumber="148" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yousefi">
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFB8EFAA41C736F18" box="[1033,1305,1353,1377]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">Asymmetricythere yousefi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="C50A4B38D37BFFEFFAA7FAA71A1F6FFB" author="BASSIOUNI" pageId="4" pageNumber="148" pagination="169 - 192" refId="ref6833" refString="BASSIOUNI, M. A. (1971) - Ostracoden aus dem Eozan von Agypten. 3. Die Unterfamilien Brachycytherinae und Buntoniinae. Geological Jahrbuch, Hannover, 89: 169 - 192." type="journal article" year="1971">BASSIOUNI, 1971</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(Eocène d’Egypte).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A12436C9D37BFFEFFCC7FA641DEC6FD8" blockId="4.[831,1437,257,1571]" box="[832,1158,1417,1442]" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">
<emphasis id="93EFEADBD37BFFEFFCC7FA641D166FDB" bold="true" box="[832,1148,1417,1442]" pageId="4" pageNumber="148">Répartition stratigraphique</emphasis>
